Andernfalls besteht die Gefahr, kostspielige globale Ungleichgewichte und sogar Zersplitterung zu schaffen.
English:
The new strategy of regional negotiations can only succeed if the TTIP and TPP are balanced and open to the wider international community and provide a foundation on which to build an international trade system. The danger is that there will be costly global imbalances and even divisions. The danger is that there will be costly global imbalances and even division.
German:
