English:
It did. Gelbers built up and became lax. Romney let it grow, and then delivered the point: “Understand the Planet.” The crowd was a crowd. The most admirable and painful moment in a grievous election campaign, perhaps, was when the effort of humanity to preserve a living planet was sparked by this moment of ominous reverence.
German:
Jede Gesellschaft umfasst solche Abweichlergruppen und -individuen, und sie verfügen heute über eine Macht, die früher unvorstellbar war.
Man denke etwa an Timothy McVeigh, der im Jahre 1995 das Murrah Federal Building in Oklahoma City in die Luft sprengte, oder an die Aum-Sekte, die im selben Jahr einen Giftgasanschlag auf die Tokioter U-Bahn verübte.
English:
Every society includes such abhorrent groups and individuals, and they today have power that was previously unimaginable. Think of Timothy McVeigh, who blew up the Murrah Federal Building in Oklahoma City in 1995, or the Aum Squad, which in the same year spewed a grenade onto the Tokyo Underground.
