English:
Perhaps Latin Americans are even asking: Are the candidates really creating food for us? After all, US corn ethanol is a huge drag on food prices, and no candidate in the presidential race seems to be recalcitrant about it. Go ahead and vote for ethanol. Go ahead and vote for ethanol. Go ahead and vote for ethanol. Given the statements the candidates have made so far about Latin America, it’s unlikely that this trend will change.
