Es ist viel einfacher, Subventionierungsprogramme zu reformieren, wenn die Wirtschaft wächst.
English:
In order to create the political space needed for economic reform, Arab leaders must conclude a regional growth package – something like a Marshall Plan – that allows large new investments and revives economic activity. It is much easier to reform subsidies if the economy is to grow.
