Damit soll jetzt Schluss sein.
English:
MADRID – Colombia, which has been caught in a long-armed struggle with the world’s most scrupulous militias since the 1960’s and has been the scene of drug lords turning its encroached rural areas into sanctuaries for crimes and unspeakable crimes, has long projected the world’s image of a bloodthirsty country. But that is not what it is now.
German:
