In jüngerer Zeit haben Wahlen in den postkommunistischen Ländern Europas Gruppen an die Macht gebracht, deren demokratische Verbundenheit, gelinde gesagt, zweifelhaft ist.
English:
Hitler, who, while his own party had the absolute majority of the votes, could not support his “combatgreifing” on a parliamentary majority. Elections in Europe’s postcommunist countries, whose democratic fervor, one remembers, are hardly a coincidence.
