Unglaublicherweise schafften es alle damals Beteiligten (ich war für Ostasien und den pazifischen Raum zuständiger Staatsekretär im Außenministerium), die intensiven Verhandlungen völlig geheim zu halten.
English:
The first two years of Carter’s presidency unfolded the saga completely out of the public’s grasp, with the exception of two significant trips to China. One was the then-external minister Cyrus Vance and the other the national security adviser Zbigniew Brzezinski, who were not with the government at the time (I was the foreign minister for East Asia and the Pacific region) to keep the intense negotiations secret.
German:
