English:
Nor is it true that social scientists are the obvious, as is sometimes claimed. On the contrary, today’s commonplaces were even more commonplaces. If you compare the terms used today to cover newspaper editorials with those used ten or more years ago, you will find the far-reaching but unaddressed impact of social sciences. It can be regretted, but it should at least be recognized.
