English:
The recent attack on the Media Center, whose television and radio stations, as well as newspapers, had been critical of the Chechen campaign, illustrates Putin’s view. The racial assault, carried out by heavily armored and masked men, was an illustration of the company’s alleged illegal actions. It was a highly illegal procedure that has so far not received any public condemnation.
